      <title>交易员认为，随着收益率飙升，美联储将等到夏季之后才会降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yields-soar-as-traders-price-in-just-two-fed-rate-cuts-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新一轮通胀加剧导致国债收益率飙升至 2024 年高点之后，投资者发出信号，美联储今年将从 9 月开始降息两次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yields-soar-as-traders-price-in-just-two-fed-rate-cuts-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑禁止向买家收取贷方产权保险费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/us-weighs-ban-on-charging-homebuyers-for-lender-title-insurance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国一家顶级消费者监管机构正在考虑是否禁止抵押贷款银行家向购房者收取保护贷方的产权保险费用，从而结束长期的行业惯例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/us-weighs-ban-on-charging-homebuyers-for-lender-title-insurance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀延迟导致新兴资产下滑 美联储降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/earnings-optimism-underpins-em-equity-gains-driven-by-ai-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国通胀数据高于预期，抑制了美联储将降息的预期，新兴市场货币下跌，股市涨幅也有所回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/earnings-optimism-underpins-em-equity-gains-driven-by-ai-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:43:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀可能推迟降息，金价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在关键通胀报告连续第三个月超过预期后，金价下跌，这表明持续的价格压力可能会将美联储的降息推迟到今年晚些时候。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/gold-holds-record-high-ahead-of-pivotal-us-inflation-figures</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 01:06:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔 500 指数受到美联储转向重新思考和战争恐慌的打击：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在另一份热门通胀报告暗示美联储今年不会急于降息后，华尔街交易员导致股票和债券下跌。随着地缘政治紧张局势再度浮现，油价攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:14:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
